    <!-- Chosen Palette: "Calm Harmony" - A base of warm neutrals (slate gray) with indigo and violet accents for a professional, tech-forward feel. -->
    <!-- Application Structure Plan: A tab-based single-page application is chosen to provide a clear, user-directed navigation path through three distinct but related concepts from the source reports. This structure prevents cognitive overload by chunking information logically. The user can choose to explore: 1) The 'Playbook' (Core PMM functions from the framework), 2) The 'Growth Roadmap' (The 18-month plan), or 3) The 'AI Advantage' (A synthesized view of AI's impact). This is more intuitive than a linear document, allowing users to access the information most relevant to their immediate needs first, while encouraging exploration of related topics. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 1. Core Pillars (Goal: Organize/Inform) -> Interactive Cards using HTML/JS. Justification: Allows users to get a high-level view and drill down into details on demand, which is better than presenting all information at once. An LLM-powered "Generate Ideas" feature is added to this section to provide dynamic, context-specific insights, enhancing engagement and practical application. 2. 18-Month Plan (Goal: Show Change/Process) -> A tabbed timeline with a dynamic Bar Chart (Chart.js). Justification: A timeline visually communicates progression, and the chart makes the evolution of KPIs tangible and easy to compare across phases. 3. AI Impact (Goal: Compare/Inform) -> A structured grid layout. Justification: Clearly contrasts GenAI vs. Agentic AI and demonstrates their specific applications across the PMM lifecycle, aiding comprehension. -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
